casebody.head_matter:
In re William Sim SPENCER, petitioner.
No. 15-7892.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 4, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of prohibition dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
